com.brashmonkey.spriter

Class Rectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.brashmonkey.spriter.Rectangle

  • public class Rectangle
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a 2D rectangle with left, top, right and bottom bounds. A rectangle is responsible for calculating its own size and checking if a point is inside it or if it is intersecting with another rectangle.
